Package: ariel
Type: Package
Title: R Front-End for the Triton GPU Compiler via MLIR
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Troy", "Hernandez", email = "troy@cornball.ai",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Translates 'torchlang' IR graphs to Triton's MLIR dialect and
    compiles them to GPU kernels. Provides R bindings for the MLIR C API
    and Triton's compilation pipeline, enabling direct GPU code generation
    from R without a Python intermediary.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    tinytest,
    torch,
    torchlang
